Use Alembic from this directory.

Commands
- Generate initial migration (autogenerate):
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/commerce alembic revision --autogenerate -m "init"
- Apply to head:
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/commerce alembic upgrade head

Inspect
- Current heads: `alembic heads`, current DB rev: `alembic current`
- Downgrade one: `alembic downgrade -1`; upgrade: `alembic upgrade head`

Notes
- env.py targets `app.models.Base` for autogenerate.
- Review autogenerate output before applying.
